query:
SELECT
                            address,
                            topic1,
                            topic2,
                            topic3,
                            topic4,
                            value,
                            miniblock_number,
                            tx_hash,
                            tx_index_in_block,
                            event_index_in_block,
                            event_index_in_tx,
                            event_index_in_block_without_eth_transfer,
                            event_index_in_tx_without_eth_transfer,
                            NULL::bytea AS "block_hash",
                            NULL::BIGINT AS "l1_batch_number"
                        FROM
                            events
                        WHERE
                            tx_hash = $1
                        ORDER BY
                            miniblock_number ASC,
                            event_index_in_block ASC
